        (40, 'Wine', 'The Tavel region in the southern Rhône Valley is renowned for which of the following wines?', 'Red', 'Rosé', 'White', NULL, 'B', 'Only rosé wines are permitted in this French appellation. '),
        (40, 'Wine', 'A dish of poached trout with a lemon sauce would pair best with which wine?', 'Chardonnay', 'Sauvignon Blanc', 'Viognier', NULL, 'B', 'The acidity of the lemon and the wine will play against each other, making the wine taste fruitier. '),
        (40, 'Wine', 'Other than Chardonnay, which of the following white wine grape varieties is among the top five being grown in Australia?', 'Riesling', 'Sauvignon Blanc', 'Sémillon', NULL, 'C', 'The others are Colombard, Muscat and Sultana. Riesling is sixth and Sauvignon Blanc is seventh.'),
