        (40, 'Wine', 'How many pounds per square inch (psi) of pressure are there on a  Champagne cork?', '10 Psi', '25 Psi', '70 Psi', NULL, 'C', 'That\'s a lot of pressure. Therefore, be careful when opening the bottle .'),
