        (50, 'Baking', 'Macaroon cookies traditionally contain which of the following?', 'Almonds', 'Hazelnuts', 'Pecans', 'Walnuts', 'A', 'Macaroons are traditionally made with ground almonds or almond paste, although sometimes they are made with coconut. '),
