        (50, 'Baking', 'Which of the following is NOT a type of Indian bread?', 'Naan', 'Poori', 'Raita', 'Roti', 'C', 'Raita is chilled yogurt seasoned with coriander, cumin, mint, cayenne pepper, caraway, and other herbs and spices. Vegetables such as cucumber and fruits like pineapple can also be added.'),
