        (50, 'Coffee/Tea', 'Antigua and Cobán are coffee varieties from which country?', 'Colombia', 'Costa Rica', 'Guatemala', 'Nicaragua', 'C', 'Both are full-bodied coffees with a spicy flavor. '),
